    "stemCode": "for(i=1; i<=n; i++)\n    for(j=1; j<=i; j++)\n        foo(i);",
    "options": [],
    "answerOptionLabels": [],
    "answerText": "n(n + 1) / 2",
    "explanation": "1 + 2 + 3 + ⋯ + n = Σ (k = 1 to n) k = n(n + 1) / 2",
